name: Katie Hyatt
body:
I'm a condensed matter physics grad student at UC Santa Barbara.
I contribute to the [Julia language](https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia), especially testing. I have a Julia package of my own, [CUSPARSE.jl](http://github.com/kshyatt/CUSPARSE.jl), which provides a Julia wrapper around the NVIDIA CUSPARSE sparse linear algebra library.
